{"tid":1541003,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Ben sir: 我屌你林鄭，係五呀","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:15:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T14:32:39.000Z","uid":230104,"like":108,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"282800294ae3cbc702655e7722bbfa193eb0f77f","tid":1541003,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsGPaeF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsGPaeF.jpg&h=8d921a37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8397fe19f0c3db0eb4f4eb1b55c324e2e21464e7","tid":1541003,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7b9e25738a9223abbde783e295bf06015d1c4e4","tid":1541003,"uid":147496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"係五啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5deed032c8d964e0e3751ac0f4aa265141543a","tid":1541003,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:20:15.000Z","msg":"個形容好貼切"},{"pid":"60d3b480258ccbc433726b140787afa777b89007","tid":1541003,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:25:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4c459083cee3daf70bad2dd2c2afd424d87e253d","tid":1541003,"uid":161313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:48.000Z","msg":"㯲錯負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af3d288f68b66dd64bf2ac725785ef43258d092","tid":1541003,"uid":34083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c459083cee3daf70bad2dd2c2afd424d87e253d","tid":1541003,"uid":161313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:48.000Z","msg":"㯲錯負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:28:05.000Z","msg":"點解而家啲人撳錯負評要講出嚟？"},{"pid":"44849652fc78cc5baedb59e3f95c6d4581673639","tid":1541003,"uid":2950,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:28:37.000Z","msg":"咁講好過出面啲唔知咩故仔<br />\n又長又沉氣"},{"pid":"69f81af14d6fb1ef06dcb850f9b1bfadbaa51491","tid":1541003,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c459083cee3daf70bad2dd2c2afd424d87e253d","tid":1541003,"uid":161313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:26:48.000Z","msg":"㯲錯負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:28:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669d7ba51f3f7564009f0585d66a2448a11ad8ae","tid":1541003,"uid":27485,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB